rows.label: qst005901_msg0001
rows.name: Nia, take a look at this.

rows.label: qst005901_msg0003
rows.name: Gula was once a prosperous republic...

rows.label: qst005901_msg0005
rows.name:
A long time ago, various
tribes in Gula gathered to
form a republic, right?

rows.label: qst005901_msg0006
rows.name:
Gula was a prosperous nation
made up of various tribes?

rows.label: qst005901_msg0007
rows.name:
I see, I see! So it was! Perhaps
I was the king who ruled Gula!

rows.label: qst005901_msg0008
rows.name:
I'm not too familiar with it, but the
chief of Torigo might know more.

rows.label: qst005901_msg0009
rows.name:
Wait a minute. Republics
don't have kings, do they?

rows.label: qst005901_msg0011
rows.name:
Let us immediately proceed
to Torigo and visit the chief
to ascertain the truth!
